{
  "version": 4,

  "_source": [
    "poe2db.tw/{us,ru}/Island_Rumours — both locales, joined on the URL slug, which is locale-invariant.",
    "",
    "`kind` is NOT our opinion and not a community rating: it is read off the game's own internal area",
    "path, which poe2db exposes (Data\\WorldAreas\\...):",
    "  ExpeditionLogBook_*     -> grand   (11: Atoll, Basin, Digsite, Gully, Heath, Peninsula, Prairie,",
    "                                      Reef, Tropical, Tundra, Wastes)",
    "  ExpeditionSubArea_*Boss -> boss    (4: Medved, Vorana, Uhtred, Olroth)",
    "  MapUnique*              -> unique  (4; Moment of Zen is one — a unique map holding a trader, which",
    "                                      poe2db's Trader ICON does not make a separate kind)",
    "  MapUberBoss_JadeCitadel -> uber    (1: The Jade Isles, Manoki)",
    "11 + 4 + 4 + 1 = 20. The eleven ExpeditionLogBook_* areas ARE the Grand Expeditions — the game says",
    "so itself. Also confirmed in-game by the user.",
    "",
    "`rumour` is the exact tooltip line, per locale — that is the string OCR reads, so it is the match key.",
    "Match after normalising: the game prints a trailing ellipsis, and OCR mangles apostrophes badly",
    "(observed: \"Nothin' to drink...\" read as \"now' to drink..\").",
    "",
    "No `mods` column, and no imported rating. The community sheet we started from had both, but it also",
    "swapped two biomes and invented a rumour that does not exist, so nothing keyed by its names can be",
    "trusted.",
    "",
    "`rating` is OURS — the owner's own judgement of how much they want to see this rumour on a tile, and",
    "the only subjective field in the file. It is deliberately a separate axis from `kind`: `kind` is an",
    "objective fact from the game, `rating` says how much YOU care. 'Boss' does not imply 'good' —",
    "Stardrinker matters because it is *Uhtred*, not because it is a boss. Scale S > A > B > C > D.",
    "null = not rated yet. Nothing here is invented: only ratings the owner stated are filled in."
  ],

  "locales": ["en", "ru"],
  "ratingScale": ["S", "A", "B", "C", "D"],

